verdict.evidence:
机制层面属实，但「用户无法就地行动」的结论被同屏常驻按钮推翻。

1) dnaEngine.ts:197-200（全量路径，targetChapterId 为空）：
  const overlimitChapters = scope.filter((c) => c.wordCount > 30000);
  if (overlimitChapters.length > 0) {
    throw new Error(`章节「${overlimitChapters[0].name}」字数已超过 30,000 字上限，...请先用剪刀裁剪成小章。`);
  }
确实在 Map 前立刻抛错。（单章精测路径 dnaEngine.ts:192-193 也有同款拦截。）

2) NovelDetail.tsx:189-207 handleExtract catch 里 setError(err.message)；错误渲染在 722-727：
  {error && (<div className="border border-red-500/20 ...">...<p className="flex-1 ...">{error}</p></div>)}
纯文本，无 onClick / 无链接 / 不调用 setManageMode —— 这部分论断准确。

3) 剪刀/拆分工具确实只在 NovelUploader（manage 视图）：✂️ 裁切 (1512)、✨ 智能语义拆分 (1219/1614/2017)、✂️ 帮我裁切 (1829/1864)；NovelDetail 提取屏内确无任何裁切控件。

4) 但关键反证：NovelDetail.tsx:331-336 头部有一颗【无条件渲染】的按钮
  <button onClick={() => setManageMode(true)} ...>章节微调裁切 ✂️</button>
它位于 322-337 的 header，在 dnaReady?... 三元(340 起)之外 → 错误红框(722-727)显示时该按钮同屏可见。即用户可一键 setManageMode(true) 跳到剪刀视图，并非死路。

5) 额外限定：✨智能语义拆分(split-recommend, index.py:729) 入口受 canSmartSplit 约束(NovelUploader.tsx:192-195: chapterCount<=1 && wordCount>=SMART_SPLIT_MIN_WORDS)，多章小说里只有单章超限时该自动入口可能不显示；但手动「✂️ 裁切」(warningType==='long'，>12000字 hover 出现, 1500-1514) 与 split 模式内「✂️ 帮我裁切」仍可用。

runResplit guard is missing the analysisStatus check (NovelUploader.tsx:921-925):
  const runResplit = async (strategy) => {
    if (!activeNovel || repairing || uploading) return;   // :922 — only repairing/uploading
    if (!window.confirm('将覆盖所有章节数据并清空 DNA 进度')) return;
    await doResplit(strategy);
  };
Contrast: handleSingleChapterExtract DOES guard it (NovelUploader.tsx:533-540): `if (activeNovel?.analysisStatus === 'mapping' || activeNovel?.analysisStatus === 'reducing') { setToast(...'已有一个全局分析任务在后台运行中'); return; }`. The asymmetry is real.

doResplit's destructive transaction (NovelUploader.tsx:839-866): `await db.chapters.where('novelId').equals(activeNovel.id).delete();` (:841) → bulkAdd new chapters with fresh `crypto.randomUUID()` ids → `db.novels.update(activeNovel.id, { analysisStatus:'idle', mapProgress:{total:0,current:0}, dnaCard:null, ... })` (:859-866). Old chapter ids destroyed; novel DNA state reset.

CRITICAL — navigating to manage view does NOT abort the running extraction (this is what would have refuted the claim, and it fails):
 - The extraction AbortController lives in NovelDetail's abortRef (NovelDetail.tsx:197-198) and is aborted ONLY by the manual pause button: `const pause = () => abortRef.current?.abort();` (:209).
 - NovelDetail's unmount cleanup clears only timers, never aborts (NovelDetail.tsx:111-114).
 - The 章节微调裁切 / 重切 button just calls `setManageMode(true)` (NovelDetail.tsx:332); store setManageMode is a bare flag flip (store.ts:215), no abort.
 - page.tsx swaps panes by conditional render — manageMode unmounts <NovelDetail/> and mounts <NovelUploader/> (page.tsx:174-177), so the runDnaExtraction promise keeps running with a never-aborted signal.

Orphan/racing writes from the still-running runner (dnaEngine.ts): worker loop does `db.chapters.update(chapter.id, {mapStatus:'mapping'})` (:271) and `{mapStatus:'error',...}` (:288) on now-deleted ids; novel-level `db.novels.update(novelId, {mapProgress:{total,current}})` (:275) and the Reduce `db.novels.update(novelId, {dnaCard, analysisStatus:'done'})` (:377) land on the just-reset novel. The repro path (deep extract running → header 章节微调裁切 → 一键智能重切 (runResplit('auto_v2'), NovelUploader.tsx:1227) → confirm) is fully reachable.

FusionWorkshop.tsx:825 — creator-page top back button: `<button onClick={() => setStep('directions')}>←</button>` — pure navigation, resets NOTHING (blocks/storyboard/sceneTexts/sceneResumeStatus all preserved). Claim's "this part is good" is correct.

FusionWorkshop.tsx:279-293 — chooseDirection() runs UNCONDITIONALLY on every card click, no guard / no equality check:
```
const chooseDirection = (direction) => {
  setDirectionTitle(direction.title);
  setBlocks({ worldviewBlock:..., protagonistBlock:..., antagonistBlock:..., narrativeTone:... }); // 281-286 overwrites blocks
  setStoryboard([]);              // 287
  setStoryboardStreamText('');    // 288
  setSceneTexts({});              // 289  <-- already-streamed prose wiped
  setSceneResumeStatus({});       // 290
  setTweakTarget('worldviewBlock');
  setStep('creator');
};
```
FusionWorkshop.tsx:789 — every direction card is wired to `onClick={() => chooseDirection(dir)}`, so re-selecting ANY card (even the same title) triggers the wipe.

FusionWorkshop.tsx:295-329 — runTweak() (the command-bar "改积木" path) touches ONLY setBlocks (309-320); it never calls setSceneTexts/setStoryboard/setSceneResumeStatus. Confirms "返回改积木不丢正文".

Grep for `confirm\(|二次确认` across the file = "No matches found" → the wipe is silent, zero confirmation. Confirms "无任何二次确认".
